HTML and CSS.
JS is also supported as a property,
if you're into that kind of thing.

<!-- @slide
escapeHtml: true
lang: www-styles
code: |
  12
  Normal <P> 0 Helvetica 12.0   1
         90 90    14.0 3.0  0  0 14    0
-->

Allow escaping HTML of unknown code
with the `slide.escapeHtml` property.

