-->

Image slides can provide
an image credit
that is distinct from any
source/citation credit for the slide.

<!-- @slide (image placeholder)
img: computer
caption: A placeholder image
-->

Placeholder images are currently
retrieved from [Lorem Picsum](https://picsum.photos/).
Maybe we can make this customizable?

